channel.title: Jaws for windows
channel.description:
Hello my name is kent davis, my older brother is blind he only became blind 7 or 8 months ago, i am trying to find him a cracked version of the software he is using now, the software he is using right now requires him to restart the computer every 15 Mins, Well anyway the name of the software is Jaws screen reading software for windows, it reads whats going on on the screen, it allows him to have Msn conversaitions with any of his friends, and many other things like check his emails. if anyone knows where i could go to get it. i have been checking as many torrent sites as possible, and all i have been getting is "Jaws the movie" again this would be very help full if anyone could help me find it so he doesnt have to restart every 15Minutes.
Regards, Kent davis.
